snippet.title: Actor Tycoon 2 [PC] Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Actor Tycoon 2 is a start-studded actor agent simulator where you play as the head of your own talent agency.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/14502/

Actor Tycoon 2 will be released on Steam soon – stay tuned for further news about its release date!
